com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface LinuxLocalUser

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, User
All Known Subinterfaces:
RedhatLinuxLocalUser, SUSELinuxLocalUser
All Known Implementing Classes:
LinuxLocalUserImpl, RedhatLinuxLocalUserImpl, SUSELinuxLocalUserImpl
public interface LinuxLocalUser
extends User

A representation of the model object 'Linux Local User'.

The following features are supported:

  • Account Description
  • Account Disabled
  • Change Password Next Logon
  • Full Name
  • Home Dir
  • Password Never Expires
  • Shell
  • User Cannot Change Password
  • User Name

See Also:
OsPackage.getLinuxLocalUser()
